verbose_text: Another report from the lab of Dr. Yong-Hui Zheng demonstrated that APOBEC3DE blocked the replication of both HIV-1 and SIV but not that of MLV and APOBEC3H inhibited the replication of HIV-1 by a cytidine deamination independent mechanism.
evidence: APOBEC3DE blocked the replication of both HIV-1 and SIV but not that of MLV
